{"tid":1832523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"求醫生指點：關於武漢肺炎癥狀","createTime":"2020-01-21T08:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T09:15:26.000Z","uid":271365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"34f1b45b9ad894caf6100c552e9b1c932135fa1f","tid":1832523,"uid":271365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:34:01.000Z","msg":"剛啱見到話武漢要管制人口流動<br />\n於是上中國國家疾控中心睇下<br />\n咁就見到幾張關於武漢肺炎病徵嘅圖<br />\n其中一張係咁（原圖係殘體字，大家唔好剷我）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9pAPuE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9pAPuE.jpg&h=8a021483&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n第三行開始係講重症嘅病徵<br />\n- 急性呼吸窘迫綜合徵<br />\n- 膿毒症休克<br />\n- 難以糾正的代謝性酸中毒<br />\n- 出凝血功能障礙<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢幾個重症病徵<br />\n我有啲疑問<br />\n想請連登嘅醫學巴絲指點下<br />\n乜野係「膿毒症休克」？因為係肺炎，咁係咪指肺部積膿引起嘅休克？<br />\n難以糾正的代謝性酸中毒，咁係咪基本上無法遏止酸中毒？乜嘢情況下先會出現咁嘅症狀？<br />\n最後嘅出凝血功能障礙，係咪會好似「伊波拉」果類內出血嘅病情？<br />\n尤其係出現後面兩種癥狀後，係咪致命率會比較高？<br />\n<br />\n利申：只係想理解多啲武漢肺炎嘅情況，唔想被官話呃<br />\n<br />\n（補返中國疾控中心條link <a href=\"http://www.chinacdc.cn/jkzt/crb/zl/szkb_11803/jszl_2275/202001/t20200121_211334.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinacdc.cn%2Fjkzt%2Fcrb%2Fzl%2Fszkb_11803%2Fjszl_2275%2F202001%2Ft20200121_211334.html&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6iKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=23e79ca6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinacdc.cn/jkzt/crb/zl/szkb_11803/jszl_2275/202001/t20200121_211334.html</a> )"},{"pid":"4d1580592e84dd1f5b28518b8baab32c3d7307a7","tid":1832523,"uid":310885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:34:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0719740d976077c756231660080101e886bf3cee","tid":1832523,"uid":24227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:42:40.000Z","msg":"膿毒症休克原來係septic shock<br />\n支那譯名睇撚死人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff5d59fe8627ec129c4b1269a25d5c5fad2210e","tid":1832523,"uid":271365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0719740d9